 get caught in my PoL and start woopin up on me...but it's not as easy as it sounds and i got tired of having to apply manaskin after every pull (they would catch up and rip it up, they hit for around 120 and fast) so i bound at the fake wall that leads to echo in shadowhaven and would just port to ec and get c2 and sow when needed...it's a pretty fast run from bind point to fungal, takes mabey at the most 5 mins including zoning (decent processor, 56k modem, 512ram) and let 'er rip from there...at first these things were dropping spells like crazy...but as of now 2:08cst 12/8 they aren't dropping 'em as fast, one every now and then...but still hella awesome xp...beats the risk of raptors and the boredom of waiting for 5 hours for a group in velks or seb just for it to disband 30 mins after you join <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :\ --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/ohwell.gif ALT=":\"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br><br>hope this helps, good luck<br><br>Tirak Energystorm<br>55 Wizard<br>&lt;Deviants of Norrath&gt;<br>Rathe Server <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umadleon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Madleon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/8/01 6:08:02 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=231.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://tyr.marietta.edu/~clanht/ho/fig/taxi.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: finally an alternative to raptors at 55</span><hr size=1> Tried it out, Lotus can cause problems and not alot of room to maneuver but definately doable. But the best spot I have seen so far is the entrance to the Grey. Golems have max 4k HP and are easily quaddable. Shissar as well.  <p><center><font face="System" size="-1"